    "created_at": "2015-06-16T08:10:48Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-16T08:10:48Z",
    "body": "Adding a new API for this is a bit tricky because JS runs in UI thread and the connection limit is set on IO thread, a callback-based API would be hard to implement and might impact performance significantly.\n\nSo instead of adding a new API I just added a `--ignore-connections-limit` switch to allow passing the domains that should ignore connections limit: \n\n``` js\napp.commandLine.appendSwitch('ignore-connections-limit', 'github.com,stream.campfirenow.com');\napp.on('ready', ...);\n```\n\nI have move your change to https://github.com/atom/brightray/commit/9541f111e9b0cb8b157b717d2d053da4d2a4f050, and it will be included in next release.\n"
  },
